    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Species of fir native to the Pacific Northwest of North America, from the extreme southeast of Alaska to the extreme northwest of California. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
